GoogleSiteSearch 1.2
Copyright (C) 2007 Ryan Finnie
http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:GoogleSiteSearch

20 Second Installation:
  1. Extract files to extensions/GoogleSiteSearch .
  2. Add the following to LocalSettings.php:
     require_once("extensions/GoogleSiteSearch/GoogleSiteSearch.php");
  3. Edit includes/SpecialSearch.php, find "function showResults( $term ) {",
     and add the following code as the first lines of the function:
        wfshowResultsGoogle( $term );
        return;
  4. That's all you need to get up and going.  Further configuration is
     possible; see: http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:GoogleSiteSearch

